Package: tRexCAP
Type: Package
Title: tRexCAP carries out 3D whole genome chromosome structure
        estimation using HiC data
Version: 1.0
Date: 2016-05-31
Author: Jincheol Park (Keimyung University, South Korea), Shili Lin (The Ohio State University, USA.
Maintainer: Jincheol Park <park.jincheol@gmail.com>
Description: tRex estimates 3D chromosome structure using three Poisson models under Bayesian framework. Truncated Random effect EXpression (tREX) mode, Poisson Random Effects Architecture Model(PRAM), Truncated Poisson Architecture Model(tPAM). A package that uses a divide and conquer strategy and the tREX algorithm as the building block for constructing whole genome three-dimensional structures.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: coda,MCMCglmm,Rcpp (>= 0.12.0),RcppArmadillo,MASS
Suggests: doParallel, doMC
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
SystemRequirements: GNU Scientific Library version >= 1.8
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
Packaged: 2026-01-06 03:22:07 UTC; webb.944
